         <abstract id="aspace_6d1066ca3266fdedf000c2f80c6c0f77">The papers consist of correspondence and orders relating to Hipolite Dumas's service in the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers. Dumas was an officer and served in New Orleans, Mobile, Virginia, and Delaware.</abstract>
